Bridge:
ebtables FORWARD -i [LAN|WLAN] -p 0x0800 --ip-src [!] address[/mask] --ip-dst [!] address[/mask] --ip-protocol [6(TCP)|17(UDP)|1(ICMP)|0(IP)] --ip-sport [!] port1[:port2] --ip-dport [!] port1[:port2] -j [DROP|ACCEPT|CONTINUE]

Router
